   Viser totalbesøk på hele domenet (megselvtonie.me)
   Bruker badge-bilde fra hits.seeyoufarm.com
*/
---

<div class="pageview">
  <img
    src="https://hits.seeyoufarm.com/api/count/incr/badge.svg?url=https%3A%2F%2Fmegselvtonie.me&count_bg=%234E763000&title_bg=%237A464600&icon=&icon_color=%23000000&title=Bes%C3%B8k&edge_flat=true"
